    <owl:Class rdf:about="http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/DOID_0080744">
        <obo:IAO_0000115 xml:lang="en">An autoimmune disease that is characterized by myositis, arthralgia, Raynaud phenomenon, mechanic hands, interstitial lung disease, and serum autoantibodies to aminoacyl transfer RNA synthetases.</obo:IAO_0000115>
        <obo:IAO_0000115 xml:lang="es">Enfermedad autoinmune que se caracteriza por miositis, artralgia, fenómeno de Raynaud, manos mecánicas, enfermedad pulmonar intersticial y autoanticuerpos séricos contra las aminoacil ARN de transferencia sintetasas.</obo:IAO_0000115>
