        <owl:annotatedTarget xml:lang="en">An autoimmune disease that is characterized by myositis, arthralgia, Raynaud phenomenon, mechanic hands, interstitial lung disease, and serum autoantibodies to aminoacyl transfer RNA synthetases.</owl:annotatedTarget>
